description:
Jeanette Fisher`s Cheering Squad would give vocal support as Jeanette entered the stadium and during her Pokémon Battles. The Cheering Squad itself is made up of some Cheerleaders, Martial Artists and Drummers.
The Cheering Squad would still cheer Jeanette on even if one of her own Pokémon had been elimated.
name: Kaoruko Ouendan
